kets\", \"from\": 456, \"to\": 463}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have all enjoyed watching the Irish athletes do us proud in Paris,\\\" Lord Mayor of Dublin James Geoghegan said.\", \"from\": 479, \"to\": 593, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 513, \"end\": 518, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999956369642543, \"rank\": 4.345096103770583e-06, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 543, \"end\": 548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999786564333, \"rank\": 2.1343528533944818e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 565, \"end\": 571, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin\", \"score\": 0.9999987864808277, \"rank\": 1.212583438145839e-06, \"text\": \"Dublin\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin\"}, {\"begin\": 572, \"end\": 587, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Geoghegan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"James Geoghegan\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Geoghegan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Geoghegan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 531, \"to\": 533}, {\"ngram\": \"Lord Mayor\", \"from\": 551, \"to\": 561}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Now is our chance to tell them in person just how proud we are of them.\", \"from\": 595, \"to\": 667, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our chance\", \"from\": 603, \"to\": 613}, {\"ngram\": \"person\", \"from\": 630, \"to\": 636}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have no doubt their efforts will have inspired lots of girls and boys all over the city and country to try and be like them some day.\", \"from\": 668, \"to\": 803, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their efforts\", \"from\": 684, \"to\": 697}, {\"ngram\": \"lots\", \"from\": 717, \"to\": 721}, {\"ngram\": \"girls\", \"from\": 725, \"to\": 730}, {\"ngram\": \"boys\", \"from\": 735, \"to\": 739}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 749, \"to\": 757}, {\"ngram\": \"country\", \"from\": 762, \"to\": 769}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So come along to O'Connell St on Monday and let us give the Irish Team a welcome home to remember!\\\"\", \"from\": 805, \"to\": 905, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 866, \"end\": 871, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999956369642543, \"rank\": 4.345096103770583e-06, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"O'Connell St\", \"from\": 823, \"to\": 835}, {\"ngram\": \"Monday\", \"from\": 839, \"to\": 845}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 854, \"to\": 856}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team Ireland Chef de Mission Gavin Noble said: \\\"Over the past few weeks our athletes have performed outstandingly, and have inspired the nation with their endeavours at the Olympic Games in Paris.\", \"from\": 907, \"to\": 1103, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 907, \"end\": 919, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999229203, \"rank\": 7.69257438597037e-11, \"text\": \"Team Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 920, \"end\": 935, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Head_of_mission\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chef de Mission\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Head_of_mission\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Head_of_mission\"}, {\"begin\": 936, \"end\": 947, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gavin_Noble\", \"score\": 0.9999958127936122, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gavin Noble\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gavin_Noble\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gavin_Noble\"}, {\"begin\": 1097, \"end\": 1102, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999786564333, \"rank\": 2.1343528533944818e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the past few weeks\", \"from\": 960, \"to\": 978}, {\"ngram\": \"our athletes\", \"from\": 979, \"to\": 991}, {\"ngram\": \"the nation\", \"from\": 1040, \"to\": 1050}, {\"ngram\": \"their endeavours\", \"from\": 1056, \"to\": 1072}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1076, \"to\": 1093}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are really proud of each and every one of them, and we would like to thank Dublin City Council for hosting such a special event to honour them.\\\"\", \"from\": 1105, \"to\": 1253, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1184, \"end\": 1203, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin_City_Council\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.874186419479028e-36, \"text\": \"Dublin City Council\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q11204\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin_City_Council\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin_City_Council\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"such a special event\", \"from\": 1216, \"to\": 1236}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Latest Paris 2024 stories Dublin City Council is asking people to use public transport when travelling to and from the family-friendly, alcohol-free event and to enter O'Connell Street from the O'Connell Bridge end.\", \"from\": 1255, \"to\": 1471, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1282, \"end\": 1301, \"tit